flowchart LR
    TRIGGER{System Events} --> NOTIF[Notification Engine]
    NOTIF --> IN_APP[In-App Notification]
    NOTIF --> EMAIL[Email Notification]
    NOTIF --> PUSH[Push Alert]

    NOTIF --> PREF{User Preferences}
    PREF -->|Opted In| DELIVER[Delivered]
    PREF -->|Opted Out| SUPPRESS[Suppressed]

    USER[Any User] --> SETTINGS[Profile Settings]
    SETTINGS --> SEC[Security / Password]
    SETTINGS --> PROF[Profile Info]
    SETTINGS --> NOTIF_PREF[Notification Preferences]